      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like a losing game though. like i'm just running on a treadmill that never stops, waiting for a feeling of connection that's never gonna come. even when i'm with people, i'm just performing. it's soul crushing. i'm just so tired of the effort it takes to stay here in this version of reality.",
